data.description: ALMOST AN ACRE! LOCATED ON LAKE BUTLER, THE CHAIN OF LAKES! Very beautiful property and amazing lakefront lot with a cute quaint home. Tall mature pine trees and oaks on the large property. Enjoy the Butler chain and Bird Island. Have fun with your family and friends skiing, wakeboarding, tubing and fishing right in your backyard. Sit near the lake and enjoy the outdoor fireplace and watching fireworks at home from the theme parks.  Only a few miles from the 429, 408 and Turnpike. Close to the theme parks and Fowlers Grove outdoor mall.
